---
layout: base.njk
title: Video Scripts
description: Outlines and scripts for upcoming TechAI Explained videos.
permalink: /video-scripts/
---

<div class="section-header">
  <h1>🎥 Video Script Outlines</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Full outlines for upcoming video content. Each includes timing, talking points, and visual direction.</p>
</div>

<div class="card-grid">
  {%- for script in collections.videoScripts -%}
  <div class="card">
    <span class="tag">Video Script</span>
    <h3><a href="{{ script.url | url }}">{{ script.data.title }}</a></h3>
    <p>{{ script.data.description }}</p>
    <div class="meta">{{ script.data.date | readableDate }}</div>
  </div>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>
